@Nederland:how dare you say that?
young pioneers are the puppets infested by Bolshevik virus bred by evil and blood, they are no better than the zombies, unless humanity awakes within them. boy scouts are the defenders of freedom and they are the first and last bulwark against Bolshevism, paid by their life and blood. they cannot be more different. they are the eternal enemies without conciliation divided by heaven and hell, godly and filthy.
My deepest scar in life is I was such a zombie before but I regretted almost sooner than everyone possible. Still, it is so deep I don't know how to fulfill, maybe only through revenge towards the evil.
